TASK_DESCRIPTION=Deep 5-domain audit of the entire Doey codebase. Domains: (1) Shell scripts, (2) Hooks, (3) Agents & Skills, (4) Go TUI, (5) Docs/Install/Cross-cutting. Each domain gets one research worker. Findings consolidated into a single structured report with severity ratings (CRITICAL/HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW), file:line references, and fix recommendations. Top 10 worst offenders highlighted. Plan ID: 25.
